OL,3,C'A death warrant': Mum's warning over
OL,4,Cson's care needs
OL,6,FFamilies have told UTV they are
OL,7,Fdevastated particularly as in many
OL,8,Fcases the carers had already been
OL,9,Fcarrying out the treatments and are
OL,10,Fgiving the only respite to families
OL,11,Ftrying to provide round-the-clock care
OL,12,Fto their loved ones.
OL,14,FLee Martin, 40, lives with very
OL,15,Fcomplex health issues and requires 24-
OL,16,Fhour care.
