OL,3,C'A death warrant': Mum's warning over
OL,4,Cson's care needs
OL,6,F"You will be signing his death warrant
OL,7,F... if you lift Lee out of home where
OL,8,Fhe's been since 2006. It's actually
OL,9,Fimprisoning him for nothing they've
OL,10,Fdone just because of their
OL,11,Fdisability," she told UTV.
OL,13,F"If Lee was institutionalised they
OL,14,Fwould be out twice as much money.
OL,15,FReally we are the experts in this.
OL,17,F"We are the ones doing to job day on
OL,18,Fday out and it's frustrating we aren't
OL,19,Frecognised for the job we do."
