OL,3,C'A death warrant': Mum's warning over
OL,4,Cson's care needs
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Western Trust
OL,7,Fsaid: "When a patient's health
OL,8,Fpresentation deteriorates, this is
OL,9,Fconsidered at that point within the
OL,10,Fcare management process.
OL,12,F"All relevant multi-disciplinary team
OL,13,Fmembers, including the patient's GP
OL,14,Fand specialist doctors involved in
OL,15,Ftheir care would be expected to
OL,16,Fcontribute to decision-making
OL,17,Fregarding how and where those specific
OL,18,Fneeds can be met.
