OL,3,C'A death warrant': Mum's warning over
OL,4,Cson's care needs
OL,6,FShe added: "I 100%, until I take my
OL,7,Flast breath, want to be able to say I
OL,8,Fcan care for my son. You can't pour
OL,9,Ffrom an empty and cup and I'm at the
OL,10,Fstage where my cup is empty and I need
OL,11,Fhelp."
OL,13,FThe Western Trust said the level of
OL,14,Fcare required for Matthew can not be
OL,15,Fdelegated to a carer, given the risks
OL,16,Finvolved.
OL,18,FIn a statement, it said: "Epilepsy
OL,19,Ftraining consists of both theory and a
OL,20,Fpractical session.
