OL,6,F"The theory component, which is
OL,7,Fsourced externally had been paused
OL,8,Fthroughout all HSC Trusts, however
OL,9,Flocally the Western Trust has resolved
OL,10,Fthis issue and local training has
OL,11,Falready recommenced.
OL,13,F"Although we can't comment on
OL,14,Findividual's treatment/care, the
OL,15,Fadministration of medication via the
OL,16,Fgastrostomy, is not a task that the
OL,17,FTrust delegate and this is based on a
OL,18,Frisk assessment.
